high_descs: Move to the right of the fridge
Pick up a cup from the counter
Move to the sink to the right
Clean the cup in the sink
Move to the coffee maker to the right of the stove
Put the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned mug on the coffee maker to the right of the stove.

high_descs: Walk straight and face the toaster on the counter.
Pick up the mug from the counter.
Turn right and take the mug to the sink.
Put the mug in the sink, wash it and take it out.
Turn left and take the mug to the coffee machine.
Put the mug in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Wash the mug and put it in the coffee machine.

high_descs: Move to stand at the counter between the fridge and dishwasher.
Pick up the white coffee mug next to the toaster.
Carry the mug to the kitchen sink.
Place the mug in the sink, turn on the water, and then remove it once washed.
Turn and carry the mug to stand in front of the coffee maker on the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the mug on the base of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Move a washed mug to the coffee maker.
